              "content": "<p style='font-size:16px;color:#cbd5e1;line-height:1.7;'>Every time a bunch of transactions happen, they get bundled into one <b style='color:#10b981;'>block</b>. That block gets a special code called a <b style='color:#f1f5f9;'>hash</b> \u2014 like a fingerprint \u2014 then gets added to the end of the chain.</p>",
